17/03/2006
SKOPJE, Macedonia -- A conference titled "Understanding the military transformation of NATO" opened on Thursday (16 March) in Skopje. This year will be very important for NATO, said General Lance L. Smith, NATO's Supreme Allied Commander Transformation in his opening remarks, adding that the November summit in Riga will cover both transformation and enlargement. At the conference, Macedonian Prime Minister Vlado Buckovski stressed the important role NATO plays in the Balkans. (MIA, Makfax - 16/03/06)
